{"tid":1624462,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"我親眼睇住你地班連登仔比人洗腦","createTime":"2019-10-05T03:57:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T04:24:12.000Z","uid":79793,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1d0fcccd49b0d0b2774386862661ddc04ec446bf","tid":1624462,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:57:45.000Z","msg":"自從呢場運動開始,我每日都凌晨5點先訓到<br />\n11點左右起一起身<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n基本上每一次大型活動之後<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>11-1點就會有幾個檢討POST</strong></span><br />\n冇咩問題,大家討論一下都好<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[red]<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但係去到3點-5點的時候,就會突然有幾個<br />\n呢樣唔好,果樣又唔好,佢好ON9,呢個又好ON9的五毛POST</span></span></strong><br />\n基本上每次都大約有300-600正評左右<br />\n<br />\n呢個鐘數,你個人會好攰,個腦分析能力會好低,好容易比人影響到<br />\n<br />\n好多人見到呢D POST就會自己開多幾個POST發表一下自己意見,去到4-5點呢個位,基本上所有POST都會圍繞係3點果幾個鬼POST到<br />\n<br />\n網軍係一定存在,<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">你自己好可能變左五毛都唔知</span></span></strong><br />\n上網唔該自己分析一下,自己諗一諗,唔好咁容易比人影響到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4149b5883779bd1f0df32cf5f9b8bf4c4d01f818","tid":1624462,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:58:42.000Z","msg":"自推(1/10)"},{"pid":"989614a24ec46b39554a721bbcad01ad6083b92e","tid":1624462,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:58:52.000Z","msg":"自推(2/10)"},{"pid":"ad4de3fad4e5802030c785d14ab143e04175f238","tid":1624462,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:59:03.000Z","msg":"自推(3/10)"},{"p